msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.268:0.2"
msgid "27. Kammapathavagga "
msgstr "27. Ways of Performing Deeds "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.268:0.3"
msgid "268. Pisuṇavācāsutta "
msgstr "268. Divisive Speech "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an4.268:1.1"
msgid "… pe … Attanā ca pisuṇavāco hoti, parañca pisuṇāya vācāya samādapeti, pisuṇāya vācāya ca samanuñño hoti, pisuṇāya vācāya ca vaṇṇaṃ bhāsati—imehi … pe …. "
msgstr "… They themselves speak divisively … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an4.268:2.1"
msgid "Attanā ca pisuṇāya vācāya paṭivirato hoti, parañca pisuṇāya vācāya veramaṇiyā samādapeti, pisuṇāya vācāya veramaṇiyā ca samanuñño hoti, pisuṇāya vācāya veramaṇiyā ca vaṇṇaṃ bhāsati—imehi … pe …. "
msgstr "… They themselves don’t speak divisively … "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.268:2.2"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

